{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":854,"text":"The first time I uttered a prayer\nwas in a glass-stained cathedral."}]},{"cues":[{"time":6403,"text":"I was kneeling long after\nthe congregation was on its feet,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9793,"text":"dip both hands into holy water,\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11703,"text":"trace the trinity across my chest,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13553,"text":"my tiny body drooping \nlike a question mark"}]},{"cues":[{"time":16379,"text":"all over the wooden pew."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18669,"text":"I asked Jesus to fix me,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21339,"text":"and when he did not answer"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23465,"text":"I befriended silence in the hopes\nthat my sin would burn"}]},{"cues":[{"time":26141,"text":"and salve my mouth"},{"time":27631,"text":"would dissolve like sugar on tongue,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":29461,"text":"but shame lingered as an aftertaste."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31376,"text":"And in an attempt\nto reintroduce me to sanctity,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34940,"text":"my mother told me of the miracle I was,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":37860,"text":"said I could grow up \nto be anything I want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40860,"text":"I decided to"},{"time":43066,"text":"be a boy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44227,"text":"It was cute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45217,"text":"I had snapback, toothless grin,\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":47007,"text":"used skinned knees as street cred,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48847,"text":"played hide and seek with \nwhat was left of my goal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51277,"text":"I was it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52204,"text":"The winner to a game \nthe other kids couldn't play,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":54629,"text":"I was the mystery of an anatomy,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":56809,"text":"a question asked but not answered,\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":58622,"text":"tightroping between awkward boy\nand apologetic girl,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":62918,"text":"and when I turned 12, the boy phase\nwasn't deemed cute anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67655,"text":"It was met with nostalgic aunts who missed\nseeing my knees in the shadow of skirts,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":73297,"text":"who reminded me that my kind of attitude\nwould never bring a husband home,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":77546,"text":"that I exist for heterosexual marriage\nand child-bearing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81168,"text":"And I swallowed their insults\nalong with their slurs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84999,"text":"Naturally, I did not\ncome out of the closet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87716,"text":"The kids at my school opened it\nwithout my permission."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90432,"text":"Called me by a name I did not recognize,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":92894,"text":"said \"lesbian,\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":94124,"text":"but I was more boy than girl,\nmore Ken than Barbie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96700,"text":"It had nothing to do with hating my body,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":98903,"text":"I just love it enough to let it go,\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":101023,"text":"I treat it like a house,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":102409,"text":"and when your house is falling apart,\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104239,"text":"you do not evacuate,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105223,"text":"you make it comfortable enough\nto house all your insides,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":109015,"text":"you make it pretty enough\nto invite guests over,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":111376,"text":"you make the floorboards\nstrong enough to stand on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115904,"text":"My mother fears I have named\nmyself after fading things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120919,"text":"As she counts the echoes\nleft behind by Mya Hall,"},{"time":123939,"text":"Leelah Alcorn, Blake Brockington."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126489,"text":"She fears that I'll die without a whisper,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128700,"text":"that I'll turn into \"what a shame\"\nconversations at the bus stop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131763,"text":"She claims I have turned myself\ninto a mausoleum,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":134409,"text":"that I am a walking casket,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136035,"text":"news headlines have turned\nmy identity into a spectacle,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":139239,"text":"Bruce Jenner on everyone's lips\nwhile the brutality of living in this body"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142995,"text":"becomes an asterisk \nat the bottom of equality pages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146541,"text":"No one ever thinks of us as human"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149637,"text":"because we are more ghost than flesh,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":151795,"text":"because people fear that\nmy gender expression is a trick,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154494,"text":"that it exists to be perverse,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156351,"text":"that it ensnares them\nwithout their consent,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":158394,"text":"that my body is a feast\nfor their eyes and hands"}]},{"cues":[{"time":161088,"text":"and once they have fed off my queer,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":163387,"text":"they'll regurgitate all the parts\nthey did not like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166387,"text":"They'll put me back into the closet,\nhang me with all the other skeletons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170747,"text":"I will be the best attraction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173162,"text":"Can you see how easy it is\nto talk people into coffins,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":176241,"text":"to misspell their names on gravestones.\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178811,"text":"And people still wonder why\nthere are boys rotting,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181266,"text":"they go away\nin high school hallways"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183657,"text":"they are afraid of becoming another\nhashtag in a second"}]},{"cues":[{"time":186559,"text":"afraid of classroom discussions\nbecoming like judgment day"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190437,"text":"and now oncoming traffic is embracing\nmore transgender children than parents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197062,"text":"I wonder how long it will be"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198807,"text":"before the trans suicide notes\nstart to feel redundant,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202487,"text":"before we realize that our bodies\nbecome lessons about sin"}]},{"cues":[{"time":206110,"text":"way before we learn how to love them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208153,"text":"Like God didn't save\nall this breath and mercy,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212077,"text":"like my blood is not the wine\nthat washed over Jesus' feet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215653,"text":"My prayers are now\ngetting stuck in my throat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220041,"text":"Maybe I am finally fixed,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223175,"text":"maybe I just don't care,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":225428,"text":"maybe God finally listened to my prayers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230139,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":231604,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}